          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-0 mt-16 border border-ink">
        <div class="border-r border-ink p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold">18+</div>
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/60 mt-1">// lat na rynku</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-r border-ink p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold">06</div>
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/60 mt-1">// obszarow uslug</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-r border-ink p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold">100%</div>
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/60 mt-1">// dedykowane</div>
        </div>
